rows.label: tlk43100342_01_msg0001
rows.name:
They say there are some monsters
that encourage their buddies to make
them stronger.

rows.label: tlk43100342_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If I was in a fight like that, I reckon it'd
be best to take out the one that was
doing the encouragement first of all.

rows.label: tlk43100342_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard that from one of my dad's
Driver buddies.

rows.label: tlk43100342_01_msg0004
rows.name:
You gotta study up if you wanna join
the Invidian army, y'know!
